The paper focuses on improving the performance of Visual Question Answering (VQA) models by reducing language biases and improving visual-explainable and question-sensitive abilities. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
